sentences: Alfred Darlington (born Alfred Weisberg-Roberts, October 31, 1977), better known by their stage name Daedelus, is an American record producer based in Los Angeles, California.
Their 2005 album, Exquisite Corpse, featured guest appearances from MF Doom, Mike Ladd, and TTC.
